HEADWORD: out-of-doors
<hw>out-of-doors</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any location outside of any
building, where the air is unconfined; the open air.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> outdoors, air, open air, open.</syn>⟦br⟧
